name: Insertion Planning
Lore: 'The Rebellion employees every advantage it has over Imperial machines. A corps of well-trained scouts can elude detection in proper terrain.',
Text: 'If your scout is in battle at an exterior planet site, subtract 3 from opponent''s total battle destiny. OR Target opponent''s character aboard an open vehicle moving to your scout''s site. Draw destiny. If destiny +2 > ability, target goes to Used Pile.',
